(1,2): positive (flip because of odd root at 1) (2,3): positive (no flip at even root 2) (3,4): negative (flip at odd root 3) (4,5): negative (no flip at even root 4) (5,6): positive (flip at odd root 5) (6,7): positive (no flip at even root 6) (7,8): negative (flip at odd root 7) (8,9): negative (no flip at even root 8) (9,10): positive (flip at odd root 9) (10, ): positive (no flip at even root 10) Wait, but hold on.
